qualifications_minimum:
1-Candidate must be working towards a doctoral degree in psychology or related field; 

2-Expertise in content area;  

3-Experience conducting and/or knowledge of play research and implementation of play in educational settings.

qualifications_preferred:
1-Preference will be given to individuals with demonstrated expertise with related course content; 

2-Demonstrated scholarship in the area of the course topic; 

3-Prior experience teaching online synchronous courses.

